Example command (kernel mode):

python scripts/generate_zoom_ics.py --select-mode kernel --grid /path/to/gridder_output.hdf5 --snap /path/to/z0_snapshot.hdf5 --ic-snap /path/to/parent_ic_snapshot.hdf5 --kernel-index 0 --target-logdelta 0.0 --parent-config configs/music2_parent_tessera.conf --template configs/music2_zoom.conf --levelmax 15 --levelmin 7 --target-rank 0

Suite driver:

python scripts/generate_zoom_suite.py suite.yml --resume
